😍😍😍😍 جمال خلق الله ❤️❤️

• When you zoom in on Amur leopards and realize their winter coat puts your Christmas sweater to shame! 🎄📸 Wishing you all a wildly merry Christmas filled with magical moments, both in front of and behind the camera! 🐾✨🐆

#Christmas #MerryChristmas #Xmas #AmurLeopard #Leopard
@nat.medlo nah Ai ain’t this good 🤭
Cant believe anything anymore cause of AI 😭
@madiprints no need in talking down to me, I have been a photographer for 50 years but the AI is all new to me, but thank you for sharing your knowledge.

@julieroland64 i wasn’t talking down to you. i was trying to be helpful - sorry if it came across that way, it was not my intention. it’s difficult over only text and no speaking to convey tone and such

@julieroland64 When I first saw this guy's videos I doubted their authenticity, but after RIGOROUS and SCIENTIFIC verification I was happy to learn they're 100% real. Definitely touched up, color graded etc., but real. Absolutely gorgeous.
This is sooo beautiful it doesn’t look 👀 real.  I hate that I doubt the authenticity of this piece.
@itseriksen Thank you very much for these very wonderful videos 💐💐💐

#Sony #SonyAlpha #SonyNordic #SonyVideo #SonyCine#Animal #AnimalVideo #planetearth #earth #NotWildlife #videography #reelsinstagram #Wildlife #WildlifeVideo #Wildlifephotography #cuteanimals #videooftheday
#bigcats #bigcat #cat #Cats 
#SonyPhotography #AnimalPhotography #wildlifephoto #EndangeredSpecies
So beautiful and beautiful as always. Merry Christmas 🎄🐯
Wow, beautiful!😍
The forbidden cars are the best
@salniter agreed and the most spicy ones🌶🤣
Beware
Cats in all sizes are perfect
Breathtakingly Beautiful ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️
@reyvan24601 I swear I'm not drunk or high.

@reyvan24601 This video definitely has a high increase in contrast. All the darks are very dark, the lights are very light. This creates a strong feeling already. The colors are also a bit more saturated than I'd assume they are in the raw footage

@reyvan24601 I believe the term you might be looking for is called “color grading”. It is a “post-production technique that changes the color, contrast, and brightness of an image to create a desired look. It's used in filmmaking and video editing to create a consistent color tone or mood.” It’s what gives movies their vibe, or feel.

OK, so I know nothing about the visual arts, so please go easy with any roasting of my naivety.... But what exactly do you do to make these colors...I don't even have the words. The colors aren't just popping; they're just more alive than life.
Gosh. That’s one gorgeous kitty. 😻
So cute yet so majestic creatures.
🎄⛄ Have a Merry Christmas
So beautiful
Magnifique ! ❤️
@olima_omega Thanks a lot man🎄🎅🏼 Merry Christmas!
Amazing 💥
The fact there are so few of these beautiful cats left makes this post more sad to me 😞😢 But these are such wonderful shots. 💖
@rowgnash I know! I wish!
@rowgnash Probably not a wild animal, but at a sanctuary
Lucky photographer
Wow! You really captured the beauty of these cats!
Stunning. Jehovah made them for our enjoyment. 🦋💜
ИИ повтори
The most beautiful video - thanks for sharing!
🐆❤️ Soooo schön
